# Application Requirements Summary

This application listens to voice commands via the microphone, matches them to predefined phrases, and executes corresponding keyboard scripts to control applications like games.

Key features include:
- Voice recognition and phrase matching
- Keyboard script execution (keystrokes, combinations, delays)
- Web interface for managing command mappings
- Real-time speech display and command testing
- Automatic recovery from failures
- State persistence across restarts

For full details, see the requirements document: [requirements.md](mdc:memory-bank/requirements.md)



